  "body": "While `All accounts` is selected, the lower toolbar featuring `Send`, `Receive`, `Bridge` and `Buy` should be removed as these actions can only be made in the context of an account.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1380\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-07-25 at 09 39 52\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/110033914/42d45e77-c986-4e49-8b76-9219efb3b264\">\r\n\r\nIn addition, there is a white stroke around the `arb1` network. The stroke should really be knocked out of the underlying network icon so the background can show through. Design can assist if needed here.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"126\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-07-25 at 09 41 47\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/110033914/f7024935-c17c-48fb-a970-3c205aaacd5b\">\r\n\r\nAnd the account hover and selection states are different for `All accounts`. The hover and selection states for `All accounts` should be the same as the other accounts.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"296\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-07-25 at 09 43 19\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/110033914/76fd4917-f581-40a1-a30e-9164c806c97c\">\r\n\r\n\r\n<img width=\"290\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-07-25 at 09 43 16\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/110033914/94e902ec-254a-4a56-959b-41d1dc87d583\">\r\n\r\n\r\nThe hover state for saved addresses is also blue but it should follow the standard hover state used for the accounts.\r\n<img width=\"305\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-07-25 at 09 46 54\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/110033914/9b753e7a-a32a-4389-abea-692ad45d9342\">\r\n\r\n\r\nThe hover states for the share address and network selector buttons are different. The chevron disappears from the network selection button on hover.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"321\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-07-25 at 09 45 00\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/110033914/cde21658-9f9f-4b5e-8844-a091942c9169\">\r\n<img width=\"287\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-07-25 at 09 45 03\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/110033914/b13bcb9a-6865-4ee6-b229-908952a152a5\">\r\n",
